      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "While St. John's Wort can be a natural mood booster, combining it with sertraline may not be the best idea. St. John's Wort can interact with many prescription medications, including antidepressants like sertraline, potentially leading to increased serotonin levels, serotonin syndrome, or reduced medication efficacy. It's recommended to consult your doctor before adding St. John's Wort to your routine, especially if you're already taking prescribed medication. They can help you assess the risks and make an informed decision.",
      "source": "target",
